snippet.textDisplay: Amazing musicians, songs, singers. Already listened to this song thousand times (no exaggeration). I would still say I love the original one little more. But nevertheless, this one is amazing too. We need to indulge our next generation more in to music so that the rich music legacy pakistan/india have continues. In my personal opinion, coke studio india has a thing or two to learn from coke studio pakistan. I follow both of them. More often I get hooked to songs from coke studio pakistan. Anyways, my knowledge about music is much more limited compared to these amazingly talented musicians, singers. Keep up the great work.
